+2001-12-22 Keith Owens  <kaos@sgi.com>
+
+	* Upgrade to 2.4.17.
+	* Clean up ifdef CONFIG_KDB.
+	* Add ifdef CONFIG_KDB around include kdb.h.
+	* Delete dummy kdb.h files for unsupported architectures.
